snippet.title: JoBlo Movie Trailers
snippet.description:
JOBLO MOVIE TRAILERS features all of the latest breaking Hollywood movie trailers, featurettes and TV spots..

The JoBlo Movie Network (www.joblo.com) was founded by a major movie nerd in his parent's garage back in 1998. Over the years, it grew into one of the most popular movie fansites in the world focused on all the latest movie news, reviews, trailers and more. In 2011, the JoBlo YouTube Network was created and continued the focus on all things movies,  including 9 channels (see links in channels tab): JOBLO TOP TRAILERS, JOBLO MOVIE CLIPS, JOBLO STREAMING/TV TRAILERS, JOBLO ANIMATED VIDEOS, JOBLO SUPERHEROES, JOBLO HORROR TRAILERS, JOBLO CELEBRITY INTERVIEWS as well as our original video content channel simply entitled JOBLO VIDEOS and JOBLO HORROR VIDEOS.

JOBLO was founded by movie fans, operated by movie fans....for movie fans!!
